title: A1708 820-00840 5V 0.16A Faulty CD3215
message:
Hello, 820-00840 board has burn mark on U3200. After U3200 replacement board still won't get 20V. Noticed that originaly U3200 was as CD3215C and i repalced it with CD3215B one. Could that be the issue?

message: I can confirm B and C and not interchangeable.
